      "writtenOn": "2017-11-29T23:46:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "These exist, but currently aren\u0027t implemented on Fuchsia (I think they\u0027ll just return -1 and set errno\u003dENOSYS). This comes up fairly frequently in calling POSIXy functions.\n\nPerhaps we\u0027d be better to just exclude this file to not mislead ourselves later.",
